Lanzhi.

00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:16.779
(Third Sister-in-law of the Xiao family)
How can you kick us when we are down?

00:02:16.780 --> 00:02:17.980
(Huo Rou)
Leaving just like this.

00:02:19.260 --> 00:02:21.220
(Second Sister-in-law of the Xiao family, Qi Lanzhi)
A daughter of the Qi family can be a widow,

00:02:21.300 --> 00:02:22.179
(Qi Lanzhi's Mother)
but she absolutely cannot be buried

00:02:22.180 --> 00:02:24.300
with a traitor
who colluded with the enemy.

00:02:24.580 --> 00:02:27.220
One never knows
when the whole family will be executed.

00:02:27.420 --> 00:02:28.699
You may not fear dying out,

00:02:28.700 --> 00:02:31.020
but we fear being dragged down by you.

00:02:31.580 --> 00:02:33.860
(Madam Xiao)
How can the Xiao family allow you to insult us at will?

00:02:33.980 --> 00:02:37.300
If you wish to leave,
you will have to step over my dead body.

00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.860
Mother, are you trying
to force me to death?

00:02:40.380 --> 00:02:41.259
Fine.

00:02:41.260 --> 00:02:42.820
Then I will die.

00:02:43.180 --> 00:02:45.620
I only beg Mother
to spare the Qi family.

00:02:52.180 --> 00:02:53.140
Fine.

00:02:53.460 --> 00:02:55.340
You are always using death
to coerce honest people.

00:02:55.540 --> 00:02:57.060
Go on, die for me then.

00:02:57.140 --> 00:02:58.620
Su Jinyuan?

00:03:01.900 --> 00:03:02.820
Fine.

00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:05.179
You are righteous.

00:03:05.180 --> 00:03:06.019
You do not fear death.

00:03:06.020 --> 00:03:07.220
But I do.

00:03:07.260 --> 00:03:08.139
Yunyao is gone.

00:03:08.140 --> 00:03:09.939
If the whole Xiao family meets disaster,

00:03:09.940 --> 00:03:12.100
who will offer incense to him
in the future?

00:03:12.140 --> 00:03:15.380
Do you want him
to wander as a lonely ghost?

00:03:16.180 --> 00:03:17.680
If you are so sentimental and righteous,

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.480
why do you not chant scriptures
and live on vegetables?

00:03:19.540 --> 00:03:20.480
Stop pretending.

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:23.000
You cling to life and fear death,
yet you still try to twist things back on us.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.640
You ran away from your marriage,
so what right do you have to judge me?

00:03:29.540 --> 00:03:30.740
(Grand Madam of the Xiao family)

00:03:40.980 --> 00:03:43.140
Since your heart is no longer
with the Xiao family,

00:03:43.260 --> 00:03:44.859
the Xiao family has not fallen so low

00:03:44.860 --> 00:03:46.620
as to force someone to stay.

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:49.300
Leave.

00:03:58.900 --> 00:03:59.940
Grandmother.

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:02.340
When I married Third Brother, I swore

00:04:02.700 --> 00:04:04.139
to share life and death,

00:04:04.140 --> 00:04:05.740
never to abandon him.

00:04:05.900 --> 00:04:07.140
Good child.

00:04:07.260 --> 00:04:09.700
If the Xiao family
cannot escape this calamity,

00:04:09.780 --> 00:04:12.780
then at least you will have something
to barter for your life.

00:04:14.300 --> 00:04:16.019
Return to your room and rest.

00:04:16.020 --> 00:04:18.780
I still have something
to say to Su Jinyuan.

00:04:20.700 --> 00:04:22.140
Yes, Grandmother.

00:04:27.060 --> 00:04:28.460
Su Jinyuan.

00:04:35.460 --> 00:04:36.980
Who allowed you to come back?

00:04:38.260 --> 00:04:39.940
What exactly are you after?

00:04:40.340 --> 00:04:41.420
Or are you here

00:04:41.660 --> 00:04:43.820
to watch a joke?

00:04:46.740 --> 00:04:47.619
Grandmother.

00:04:47.620 --> 00:04:48.539
Mother.

00:04:48.540 --> 00:04:49.739
I fled from my marriage first,

00:04:49.740 --> 00:04:51.300
bringing shame upon the Xiao family.

00:04:51.460 --> 00:04:52.860
I know I grave mistake

00:04:53.220 --> 00:04:54.660
and has come to atone.

00:04:54.980 --> 00:04:56.019
I know full well

00:04:56.020 --> 00:04:58.220
I no longer have the face
to stand before the Xiao family.

00:04:58.380 --> 00:05:00.179
When I heard the Xiao family
was in trouble,

00:05:00.180 --> 00:05:01.739
I wished to offer
what little help I could.

00:05:01.740 --> 00:05:03.020
Do not call me Mother.

00:05:03.140 --> 00:05:04.380
It disgusts me.

00:05:04.620 --> 00:05:06.260
Even if the Xiao family falls,

00:05:06.420 --> 00:05:08.060
we do not need your charity.

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:10.260
Get out.

00:05:12.020 --> 00:05:13.819
Young Master Xie was taken

00:05:13.820 --> 00:05:15.300
by Luo Yu to protect the Xiao family.

00:05:16.100 --> 00:05:17.420
What did you say?

00:05:19.020 --> 00:05:20.619
I thought Yan was outside

00:05:20.620 --> 00:05:21.980
and could escape this calamity.

00:05:22.340 --> 00:05:23.419
I did not expect him

00:05:23.420 --> 00:05:25.180
to fall into Luo Yu's hands after all.

00:05:25.380 --> 00:05:26.620
They truly intend

00:05:26.780 --> 00:05:28.420
to wipe out the Xiao family

00:05:28.700 --> 00:05:31.500
without leaving
a single one of us alive.

00:05:32.700 --> 00:05:34.100
Yan

00:05:34.820 --> 00:05:36.460
has little chance of survival this time.

00:05:38.100 --> 00:05:39.059
Madam,

00:05:39.060 --> 00:05:40.300
what matters most now

00:05:40.420 --> 00:05:42.340
is to find Young Master Xie
as soon as possible

00:05:42.420 --> 00:05:44.220
and let him know
what has happened at Xiao Manor.

00:05:44.460 --> 00:05:45.899
Otherwise I fear he will be deceived

00:05:45.900 --> 00:05:47.860
and may choose to end his life.

00:05:47.980 --> 00:05:49.220
If that truly happens,

00:05:50.380 --> 00:05:52.180
there will be no saving him.

00:05:53.260 --> 00:05:54.820
I came prepared this time.

00:05:55.420 --> 00:05:57.460
I brought both money and medicine.

00:05:58.260 --> 00:05:59.180
Grand Madam,

00:05:59.340 --> 00:06:01.660
is there a way for you
to send me to see Young Master Xie?

00:06:07.420 --> 00:06:09.420
Why do you want to help the Xiao family?

00:06:09.940 --> 00:06:12.419
Do you know that
if you enter the Imperial Prison,

00:06:12.420 --> 00:06:14.539
it will be
a one in ten thousand chance to survive?

00:06:14.540 --> 00:06:16.740
Do you not fear being implicated
by the Xiao family,

00:06:17.100 --> 00:06:19.140
and executed along
with your entire clan?

00:06:27.220 --> 00:06:28.380
I am not afraid.

00:06:30.180 --> 00:06:31.900
I have already died once.

00:06:33.260 --> 00:06:34.379
This life I have now

00:06:34.380 --> 00:06:36.140
is meant to be returned
to the Xiao family.

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:46.139
If I go

00:06:46.140 --> 00:06:47.340
and never return,

00:06:48.100 --> 00:06:49.419
I ask only that you two Madams

00:06:49.420 --> 00:06:50.899
help take care of my parents.

00:06:50.900 --> 00:06:53.380
(Tablet of Beloved Father Su Wansheng
and Beloved Mother Cheng Wanru)

00:06:54.580 --> 00:06:56.220
As their daughter in this life,

00:06:56.220 --> 00:06:58.860
I have never once repaid my parents
with even the smallest filial piety.

00:07:01.620 --> 00:07:02.619
I, Su Jinyuan,

00:07:02.620 --> 00:07:03.779
has no regrets even in death,

00:07:03.780 --> 00:07:05.940
so long as I can repay the Xiao family.

00:07:07.540 --> 00:07:08.660
Mother,

00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:10.740
Grandmother,

00:07:11.300 --> 00:07:12.740
please let me go.

00:07:29.500 --> 00:07:30.820
Since that is your resolve,

00:07:31.460 --> 00:07:33.300
the jailer Yang Hong
of the Imperial Prison

00:07:33.380 --> 00:07:35.860
once served
under the Xiao family's forces.

00:07:39.700 --> 00:07:40.820
Take this.

00:07:42.420 --> 00:07:44.499
I hope he will find a way

00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:46.540
to bring you to see Yan.

00:07:55.260 --> 00:07:58.180
We will take care of your parents.

00:07:58.220 --> 00:08:01.380
The Xiao family
will see to them properly.

00:08:01.420 --> 00:08:03.100
Are you willing?

00:08:07.220 --> 00:08:10.100
I will not fail Grandmother's trust.

00:08:34.020 --> 00:08:34.900
Mother,

00:08:35.140 --> 00:08:37.820
for her to come to the Xiao family now
she must have an agenda.

00:08:48.820 --> 00:08:51.020
Since she dares to wager her life,

00:08:51.460 --> 00:08:52.740
the Xiao family

00:08:52.820 --> 00:08:54.460
cannot refuse her.

00:08:55.780 --> 00:08:56.860
This time,

00:08:57.540 --> 00:08:58.860
I will trust her.

00:09:09.460 --> 00:09:11.320
You will have only the time
of one incense stick.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:12.339
Say what you must quickly.

00:09:12.340 --> 00:09:13.340
All right.

00:09:30.380 --> 00:09:31.780
Young Master Xie,

00:09:32.140 --> 00:09:33.099
Young Master Xie,

00:09:33.100 --> 00:09:34.580
it is me.

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:39.020
It is me.

00:09:43.580 --> 00:09:44.700
Are you all right?

00:09:47.140 --> 00:09:48.380
Why are you here?

00:09:50.420 --> 00:09:52.859
The Grand Madam of the Xiao family
sent me to bring you medicine.

00:09:52.860 --> 00:09:54.060
I must not use medicine.

00:09:55.060 --> 00:09:56.419
If Luo Yu discovers it,

00:09:56.420 --> 00:09:57.900
