00:10:04.060 --> 00:10:05.179
This is Heart-Saving Pellet.

00:10:05.180 --> 00:10:07.020
It can save your life
in a critical moment.

00:10:15.580 --> 00:10:16.940
Sir Luo,

00:10:17.340 --> 00:10:18.699
what brings you here so late?

00:10:18.700 --> 00:10:19.059
Quick,

00:10:19.060 --> 00:10:20.620
hide.

00:10:31.100 --> 00:10:33.260
General Xie is in
such good spirits today.

00:10:33.340 --> 00:10:35.620
You did not even curse
at the sight of me.

00:10:37.100 --> 00:10:39.459
It seems you have finally
come to your senses.

00:10:39.460 --> 00:10:41.419
Your Xiao family
has colluded with the enemy,

00:10:41.420 --> 00:10:43.820
none of you will escape death.

00:10:46.700 --> 00:10:48.419
Do you still think
you are the Sixth Master Xie

00:10:48.420 --> 00:10:50.580
protected by Prince Duan?

00:10:50.900 --> 00:10:52.899
Hand over the Xiao family's
private seal obediently,

00:10:52.900 --> 00:10:55.260
and I may spare your life.

00:10:59.060 --> 00:11:00.820
(The private seal?)

00:11:01.100 --> 00:11:02.380
(The Xiao family?)

00:11:05.580 --> 00:11:06.980
You want the private seal

00:11:07.380 --> 00:11:09.780
because you wish to fabricate charges
against the Xiao family.

00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:11.099
It shows you still cannot

00:11:11.100 --> 00:11:13.180
fully convict the Xiao family.

00:11:14.060 --> 00:11:15.980
How could I, for my own safety,

00:11:16.740 --> 00:11:18.580
harm a household of loyal men.

00:11:20.860 --> 00:11:22.500
Still stubborn at death's door.

00:11:22.740 --> 00:11:23.779
I want to see

00:11:23.780 --> 00:11:24.979
