00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:08.700
that dog.

00:12:22.220 --> 00:12:25.420
Do you truly think I dare not kill you?

00:12:30.500 --> 00:12:32.659
Sir Luo, there are orders from above.

00:12:32.660 --> 00:12:34.540
We must not cause a death.

00:12:42.020 --> 00:12:45.140
Xie Yunyan, I will spare you for now.

00:12:45.580 --> 00:12:47.659
Do not think you can keep your life.

00:12:47.660 --> 00:12:49.019
You may escape today,

00:12:49.020 --> 00:12:51.100
but let's see if you can
still live past the next.

00:13:01.820 --> 00:13:03.499
You know he wants your life.

00:13:03.500 --> 00:13:05.180
Why would you provoke him?

00:13:05.380 --> 00:13:06.579
If something happened to you,

00:13:06.580 --> 00:13:08.100
what would we do?

00:13:10.180 --> 00:13:12.020
He does not dare truly act.

00:13:13.380 --> 00:13:14.700
Regardless of that,

00:13:15.340 --> 00:13:17.140
you cannot be harmed.

00:13:17.620 --> 00:13:18.819
In this situation,

00:13:18.820 --> 00:13:19.779
